OL,3,CGreens vow tax hike on richest in
OL,4,Cmanifesto to 'mend broken Britain'
OL,6,FThe Greens attacked both Labour and
OL,7,Fthe Conservatives when they launched
OL,8,Ftheir manifesto on Wednesday, ITV
OL,9,FNews' Political Reporter Jasmine
OL,10,FCameron-Chileshe reports.
OL,12,FWords by James Gray, ITV News Producer
OL,14,FThe Green Party has pledged to end the
OL,15,F"conspiracy of silence" around tax,
OL,16,Fpromising to raise more money from the
OL,17,Fwealthy as it unveiled its manifesto
OL,18,Ffor the General Election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
