OL,6,FThe tax on multimillionaires and
OL,7,Fbillionaires will be used to fund
OL,8,Fimprovements to health, housing,
OL,9,Ftransport and the green economy, the
OL,10,Fparty said.
OL,12,FGreen Party co-leader Adrian Ramsay
OL,13,Fsaid the party - which launched its
OL,14,Fmanifesto in Brighton and Hove on
OL,15,FWednesday - wants to create a fairer
OL,16,Fsystem and ask those "with the
OL,17,Fbroadest shoulders to pay more".
