OL,6,FHe attacked both Labour and the
OL,7,FConservatives for hiding plans to cut
OL,8,Fpublic services rather than
OL,9,Fconfronting "the need for a fairer tax
OL,10,Fsystem."
OL,12,FHere, ITV News explains the key
OL,13,Fpolicies the Greens unveiled as part
OL,14,Fof their manifesto.
OL,16,FWatch a summary of the key
OL,17,Fannouncements made by Green Party co-
OL,18,Fleaders Carla Denyer and Adrian Ramsay
OL,19,Fat the launch of their party's General
OL,20,FElection manifesto
