OL,4,Cmanifesto to 'mend broken Britain'
OL,6,FThe party's manifesto said it would
OL,7,Fintroduce a Wealth Tax of 1% annually
OL,8,Fon assets above #10 million and of 2%
OL,9,Fon assets above #1 billion.
OL,11,FAmong other measures, it also pledged
OL,12,Fto reform Capital Gains Tax to "align
OL,13,Fthe rates paid by taxpayers on income
OL,14,Fand taxable gains", as well as remove
OL,15,Fthe Upper Earnings Limit, which
OL,16,F"restricts the amount of National
OL,17,FInsurance paid by high earners".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
