OL,6,FThe party estimates that these
OL,7,Fmeasures could raise "additional
OL,8,Frevenue of between #50 and #70 billion
OL,9,Fper year in 2024 prices".
OL,11,FThe Greens also said "privatisation
OL,12,Fhas failed" and promised to bring
OL,13,Fwater companies, railways and the five
OL,14,Fbig retail energy companies into state
OL,15,Fownership.
OL,17,FGreen Party co-leader Carla Denyer
OL,18,Fsaid her party's manifesto is "based
OL,19,Fon investing to mend broken Britain
OL,20,Fand offer real hope and real change".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
