OL,6,FShe added: "At the heart of this would
OL,7,Fbe a tax on the very richest, the top
OL,8,F1% of people requiring them to pay a
OL,9,Fbit more into the pot.
OL,11,F"From the Tories and Labour, we've
OL,12,Fbeen hearing a race to the bottom on
OL,13,Ftax.
OL,15,F"They think two pence off here and a
OL,16,Fpenny off there will impress voters
OL,17,Fand they think that people won't
OL,18,Fcotton on that this means even more
OL,19,Fdevastating cuts to public services
OL,20,Flike the NHS that we rely on every
OL,21,Fday."
