OL,6,FMr Ramsey said the climate crisis has
OL,7,Fbeen "pretty much absent from this
OL,8,Felection campaign so far".
OL,10,F"The other parties are running away
OL,11,Ffrom their promises on climate. Only
OL,12,Fthe Greens understand that the
OL,13,Fsolutions to the climate crisis are
OL,14,Falso the solutions to the cost-of-
OL,15,Fliving crisis," he added.
OL,17,F"The climate crisis is the most
OL,18,Fserious we face as a global community.
OL,19,FOur commitment to you is that
OL,20,Fprotecting our climate and nature lies
OL,21,Fat the heart of all of our policies."
